               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Bāb al-ḥādī ʿashr by Afz̤al al-Dīn Muḥammad ibn Taqi al-Din Muḥammad ibn Ghiyās̤ al-Dīn Maḥmūd al-Ḥasanī al-Ḥusaynī Mūsavī al-Shahristānī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008111616 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85121424" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_239-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic </textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Untitled Persian translation and commentary by <persName key="person_f8067" role="trl cmm">Afz̤al al-Dīn Muḥammad ibn Taqi al-Din Muḥammad ibn Ghiyās̤ al-Dīn Maḥmūd al-Ḥasanī al-Ḥusaynī Mūsavī al-Shahristānī</persName> on the treatise addressing Shīʿī theological questions, entitled <title key="work_22189">Bāb al-ḥādī ʿashr</title>, by <persName key="viaf_90059858" role="ant">Shaykh Abū al-Qāsim Najm al-Dīn Jaʿfar ibn Ḥasan ibn Yaḥyá al-Ḥillī</persName>, known as the <persName key="viaf_90059858">Muḥaqqiq al-Ḥillī</persName> (d. 676/1277). 
                        </p>
                        <p>Not dated at end. 
</p>
                        <p>Nastaʿlīq; Arabic quotations in awkward naskh overlined in red. 
</p>
                        <p>Stamped foliation. 
</p>
                        <p>Binding damaged (combed marble papers over pasteboards edged with leather; spine detached), labels removed. 
</p>
                        <p>Folios mostly bound; occasional wormholes. 
</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f8067">Afz̤al al-Dīn Muḥammad ibn Taqi al-Din Muḥammad ibn Ghiyās̤ al-Dīn Maḥmūd al-Ḥasanī al-Ḥusaynī Mūsavī al-Shahristānī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="person_f8067">افضل الدّين محمّد ابن تقى الدّين محمّد ابن غياث الدّين محمود الحسنى الحسينى الموسوى الشّهرستانى</persName>
